snippet.title: Polygon Runway
snippet.description:
Polygon Runway is a educational channel of Roman Klčo, designer and illustrator, 10+ years in business.
Don't miss out and offer your clients something new. Subscribe to learn how to make 3D illustrations and use 3D in design.

Releasing new videos on Wednesday and Friday.


You can see some of my work on dribbble.com/romanklco
